text:
Too many bad actors in the firearms industry are getting away with illegal gun sales while Americans pay the price.

@RepDean and I are calling for @ATFHQ to hold gun dealers accountable and better enforce our nation's gun laws.

People deserve to feel safe.

Protecting our most basic freedoms should not be partisan in the least. 

@HouseDemocrats stand with @POTUS in our fight to enact HR4, the John Lewis Voting Rights Advancement Act and the Freedom to Vote Act. 

Our very democracy is at stake.

The melting of our polar caps is irreversible. 

We can't turn back the clock but by reducing our carbon emissions, we can still save our planet. 

@HouseDemocrats passing the Build Back Better Act, is perhaps our best shot at doing so. https://t.co/Grl5dfs7Sf

We're recovering from a pandemic and the worst economic downturn since 2008.

@POTUS promised that in the wake of that disaster, he would rebuild our middle class and ensure that families never fall behind again.

#BuildBackBetter delivers on that promise. https://t.co/F1R9izWrlb
